text: Jean-Julien Rojer and Horia Tecău were the two-time defending champions, but chose not to participate this year. Łukasz Kubot and Marcelo Melo won the title, defeating Nicholas Monroe and Tennys Sandgren, 6–7(6–8), 6–1, [10–3]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== ==Sources== * Main Draw Winston- Salem Open - Doubles 2019 Doubles
